Lubitz is believed to have sought help with his vision problems as recently as March 10. Police have revealed they found evidence at his home to suggest he suffered from a serious 'psychosomatic illness.' 

His former girlfriend described him as an erratic and controlling man, who would frequently wake up with nightmares. 

In a chilling premonition she said he once told her ‘One day I will do something that will change the whole system, and then all will know my name and remember it.’

